data.description: Enjoy this Courtyard Villa with stunning water front views.  Rest assured this villa boasts a NEW 2023 Roof, a completely renovated 2023 kitchen with white shaker style cabinets, glass subway tile backsplash and granite countertops.  Originally a 3 bedroom this villa was thoughtfully converted to a 2 bedroom villa to create a spacious open concept living area with direct water views, laminate flooring, high volume ceilings boasting water views and lots of ambient light.  Washer and dryer are in the unit. NO ASSOCIATION APPROVAL REQUIRED.  This is an ALL AGES, pet friendly community, located close to Boca Schools, houses of worship, shopping and dining. New roof 2023! Olympic Heights Community H.S.Whispering Pine ElementaryOmni Middel School
